\frac{x^4} {(x-1)^3}
 \frac{x^4} {(x-1)^3}=\frac{A}{x-1} + \frac{B}{(x-1)^2} + \frac{C}{(x-1)^3}
(x-1)^3
x^4=A(x-1)^2+B(x-1)+C
x^4=Ax^2-2Ax+A+Bx-B+1
x+3+\frac{6}{x-1}+\frac{4}{(x-1)^2}+\frac{1}{(x-1)^3}
\dfrac{x^4}{(x - 1)^3}
\dfrac{x^4}{x^3 - 3x^2 + 3x - 1}
\begin{aligned} \dfrac{x^4 - x(x^3 - 3x^2 + 3x - 1)}{x^3 - 3x^2 + 3x - 1} &= x + \dfrac{x^4 - x^4 + 3x^3 - 3x^2 - x}{x^3 - 3x^2 + 3x - 1}\\ &= x + \dfrac{3x^3 - 3x^2 - x}{x^3 - 3x^2 + 3x - 1}\\ &= x + 3 + \dfrac{3x^3 - 3x^2 - x - 3(x^3 - 3x^2 + 3x - 1)}{x^3 - 3x^2 + 3x - 1}\\ &= x + 3 + \dfrac{6x^2 - 8x + 3}{x^3 - 3x^2 + 3x - 1} \end{aligned}
x + 3 + \dfrac{6}{x - 1} + \dfrac{4}{(x - 1)^2} + \dfrac{1}{(x - 1)^3}
\,x^3/(x\!-\!1)^3
\,x = (x\!-\!1) + 1.\,
 
\ t = x\!-\!1,\ 
 \dfrac{x^4}{(x\!-\!1)^3}\, =\, \dfrac{(t\!+\!1)^4}{t^3}\, =\, \dfrac{(t^4\! + 4 t^3\!+6t^2\!+4t+1}{t^3}\, =\, t +4+\dfrac{6}{t}+\dfrac{4}{t^2}+\dfrac{1}{t^3}
\, t = x\!-\!1\,
